<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.276942>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. 1, Andraegoidus translucidus sp. nov. male (dorsal view, holotype); 2, Andraegoidus translucidus sp. nov. male (lateral view, holotype); 3, Andraegoidus homoplatus male (holotype of T. homoplatus); 4, Andraegoidus homoplatus male (holotype of A. hassenteufeli); 5, Andraegoidus lacordairei male; 6, Andraegoidus lacordairei male (holotype of A. lacordairei punctipennis)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/276942/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

